The title of Knight is bestowed upon thee...

00:08:20.959 --> 00:08:21.752
Nonsense!
The title of Knight is bestowed upon thee...

00:08:21.752 --> 00:08:22.127
The title of Knight is bestowed upon thee...

00:08:22.127 --> 00:08:23.462
They would be thieves without war.
The title of Knight is bestowed upon thee...

00:08:23.462 --> 00:08:23.712
